---
const dashboardImg = "/educational_dashboard_app_1778817181108.png";
const classroomImg = "/kids_studying_together_1778817129229.png";
---

<section class="py-32 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-24">
      <span class="text-purple-500 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-4 block">Learning Solutions</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight">
        Explore Our <span class="text-teal-400 underline decoration-amber-500 underline-offset-8">Curriculum</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 1: Image Left -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-20 mb-40">
      <div class="flex-1 relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-purple-600/20 blur-[80px] rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="relative p-4 bg-purple-600 rounded-[4rem] rotate-[-3deg] shadow-2xl">
          <img src={classroomImg} alt="Session" class="w-full h-[450px] object-cover rounded-[3.5rem]" />
          <div class="absolute top-10 -left-10 bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl max-w-[200px] hidden lg:block animate-pulse">
            <p class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-sm">Mentoring Session Live Sekarang! 🚀</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <span class="text-purple-400 font-bold text-sm mb-4 block uppercase tracking-widest">01. One-on-One Tutoring</span>
        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8 leading-tight">Personalized Sessions for Every Subject</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Setiap siswa mendapatkan perhatian penuh dari mentor AI dan fasilitator manusia untuk memastikan tidak ada materi yang tertinggal.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          {["Pilihan Jadwal Fleksibel", "Materi Adaptif", "Laporan Progres Real-time"].map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-200 font-medium">
              <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-500/20 text-teal-400 flex items-center justify-center text-xs">✓</span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 2: Image Right -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-20">
      <div class="flex-1 relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-amber-500/20 blur-[80px] rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="relative p-4 bg-amber-500 rounded-[4rem] rotate-[3deg] shadow-2xl">
          <img src={dashboardImg} alt="Pace" class="w-full h-[450px] object-cover rounded-[3.5rem]" />
          <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 bg-slate-900 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl max-w-[220px] hidden lg:block">
            <p class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Pace Belajar: Optimal ⚡</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-2">Berdasarkan gaya belajarmu minggu ini.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <span class="text-amber-400 font-bold text-sm mb-4 block uppercase tracking-widest">02. Adaptive Learning</span>
        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8 leading-tight">Learn at a Pace That Works for You</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Jangan terburu-buru, atau jangan menunggu. Sistem kami mendeteksi tingkat pemahamanmu dan menyesuaikan tantangan berikutnya secara otomatis.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="p-6 bg-slate-900/50 border border-white/5 rounded-3xl">
            <span class="text-2xl mb-2 block">⚡</span>
            <p class="text-white font-bold">Fast Lane</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Untuk topik yang kamu kuasai.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-slate-900/50 border border-white/5 rounded-3xl">
            <span class="text-2xl mb-2 block">🐢</span>
            <p class="text-white font-bold">Deep Dive</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Sabar di materi yang menantang.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
